    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> But be careful, the order in which input, change, keypress, keyup and keydown are fired is tricky.\n\nSo I wonder, @pixelastic can't we just use 'input' event for everything (it would handle keyup, change, paste..).\n\nThen the only missing part would be that on IE9, deleting would not produce a new search, we can fix that separately.\n",
